summary: A basic tower on the banks of the largest lake in Skyrim. Its a very simple design but has all the basics: Smithing areas such as a blacksmihts forge and workbench. It has a place to sleep and player storage. located in a relaxed area it is the perfect place to sit back and enjoy the water.
descriptionHtml: A basic tower on the banks of the largest lake in Skyrim. Its a very simple design but has all the basics: Smithing areas such as a blacksmihts forge and workbench. It has a place to sleep and player storage. located in a relaxed area it is the perfect place to sit back and enjoy the water. this mod is my first mod and I will try to improve it as my moding skill progress. Also, there is a good spot to test your eye for archery. see if you can find it.
